createSubSet

public void createSubSet(OWLGraphWrapper targetGraph,
                         Set<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClass> subset,
                         Set<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntology> toMerge)
                  throws org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyCreationException
Given a collection of classes (such as those generated from a reasoner getSubClasses call), create a subset ontology and place it in targetGraph. The subset ontology is created by first collecting all axioms from toMerge that form a description of the input subset classes, adding these to the target ontology, and then including the reference closure via Mooncat

Parameters:
targetGraph -
subset -
toMerge -
Throws:
